. We also develop a condition based on relaxed criteria for achieving\nconsensus on velocity or heading angle of the mobile robots. Our validation\napproach is based on mathematical arguments and extensive computer simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2016 18:59:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-30"}
