ally, after the FWHM correction, the\nAGN black hole mass estimates from CIV closely match the DR7Q ones (with the\ndispersion of 0.28 dex), and more importantly the MgII and CIV BH masses agree\ninternally with the mean offset of 0.07 dex and the dispersion of 0.39 dex.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2016 19:53:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-25"}
