al pull of the Sun turn out to be of the\norder of 1', oscillations in obliquity can be estimated to be of the order of\n0.5'.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Sep 2016 15:26:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-03"}
